{"tid":2346573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府：會嚴格按照共產黨規定處理美國賣買物業事宜 提醒各界應留意規定避免損失","createTime":"2020-12-30T10:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T11:18:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"05e053a572376aca0b795788dc7190694a81fb1f","tid":2346573,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"外交部：美駐港總領事館出售物業要先得到中方同意 特區政府：會嚴格按規定行事<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部回應指，交易要先得到中方同意。發言人汪文斌表示，鑒於美方對外國駐美使領館房地產管理規定，根據對等原則，中方要求美國駐華使領館，包括駐港總領館，在租賃、購置、出售或以其他任何方式獲得或處置房地產，以及實施館舍新建、改建、擴建、修繕等工程時，亦必須相應提前向中方提出書面申請，並提供詳細信息。得到中方書面答覆同意後，方可辦理有關手續。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府指，按中央政府規定，根據對等原則和中方相關房地產管理要求，美國政府要就交易提前經外交部駐港特派員公署，向中央政府提出申請，土地註冊處因而致函恆隆地產代表律師說明情況，強調會嚴格依照中央政府就美國駐華使領館處置房地產的規定行事，提醒任何企業和人士留意有關規定，避免蒙受不必要損失。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2372776&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=a495abae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372776</a>"},{"pid":"38854d3a5a2c032031f6ddb42c6af0d8eb2cfe2c","tid":2346573,"uid":175673,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:57:47.000Z","msg":"支持凍結所有美國在港資產。<br />\n加速唔好縮。"},{"pid":"5808a830ef8ec3f888f282e2c7b779f5088fef21","tid":2346573,"uid":237425,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"賣樓都關外交事務事<br />\n外資又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f48979607023f8afb5e6c4958ea4822d123fab","tid":2346573,"uid":361247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"唔比賣=美國領土"},{"pid":"006ea12c5a95986acbe45b19e268fef5d8ca00d6","tid":2346573,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"睇下唔畀美國領事館賣地傷啲<br />\n定係禁哂支那股赴美上市傷啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7410464fab31d88f46d75aac54efcf2495d451e0","tid":2346573,"uid":124623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"關咩外交事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買棟樓比自己staff住，唔通住領事館咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔比而家cut人手，或者部署撤出香港，唔比賣返走棟樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中聯辦咪又係私人市場同四叔買成棟樓做宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都唔係叫香港政府特登批地起樓做宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再者，佢呢個物業有比足香港政府天價差餉、地稅ga wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇優待ga wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同私人物業冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c8f123d3510cd6650c893d37dda0222bb56765","tid":2346573,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79d4684748d16d65a98a65d11893fdc49a18f2d9","tid":2346573,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ba13919380e3f545e849ea4e7fbcf55fa14